text: Strong with Spirit () is a 1967 Soviet movie directed by Viktor Georgiyev.Кинотеатрам бесплатно предоставят фильмы о Великой Отечественной войнеСИЛЬНЫЕ ДУХОМ (1967) It stars Gunārs Cilinskis, Ivan Pereverzev, and Yevgeni Vesnik. ==Actors== * Gunārs Cilinskis as Nikolai Kuznetsov / Paul Zibert * Ivan Pereverzev as Dmitry Medvedev * Yevgeni Vesnik as Voronchuk, agent * Lyusyena Ovchinnikova as Galya * Yuri Solomin as Mayor Gettel * Vija Artmane as Lidia Lisovskaya == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet movies Category:1967 movies
title: Strong with Spirit
